first of all, this release is on other trackers than swebits... actually it came on swebits quite late. also bittorrent itsn't the only way to get dvdr, in case you wonder....
second, if you had read the faq on swebits, you would know that it says this: "Att skapa en ny torrent av det du laddat ner och ladda upp på annat ställe går däremot naturligtvis utmärkt."
So I really can't se the problem in what he's doing... he just spreading joy to more people. And since the swebits isn't an open site, I could imagine that many people is appreciate what he's doing.

But I must say, you did accomplish to seem VERY cool and leet, knowing where this release came from!
